"'''The Crypt of Saalo Morn'''" was a web enhancement published at [[Wizards.com]] on [[July 26]], [[2001]] for the ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]'', to be used with ''[[The Dark Side Sourcebook]]''.

{{Game-stub}}

==Plot summary==
A group of adventurers explore the ancient crypt of long dead self-proclaimed [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]] [[Saalo Morn]], haunted by Morn's [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] spirit.

